description.en:
The Thanos team at it’s core has always focused on innovation, from humble beginnings of developing community owned coins. Through our experience and thirst for innovation we have developed a revolutionary way for investors to profit without being taxed on transactions. 

Thanos is a fair launched token that serves the community of crypto via our safe and secure  Vault. The Vault provides 75% of all Liquidity Locker fees to holders as ETH rewards.

Thanos is here to rewards its holders through our liquidity locker Vault.
